---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import GreenBlock from '../components/GreenBlock.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Contact"
  description="Question about MPower, or a partnership that genuinely helps people? Email a human. MPower doesn't sell sponsorships, run ads, or carry affiliate deals."
>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mono kicker">§ Contact &amp; partnerships · 2026</div>
      <h1 class="display contact-h1">
        Come and <span class="i-accent">say kia ora.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg contact-lede">
        One email. One straight answer. No phone tree, no ticket number, no chatbot. Tell us what you need and a real human comes back to you.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-ctas">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:askme@mpowerhq.nz">askme@mpowerhq.nz <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <hr class="rule" />
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="mono accent">§ 01 · Email us</span>
          <h2 class="heading contact-col-title">One address. A real human.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="prose">
          <p>For anything and everything MPower - a general question, a team you want it built around, a partnership or a sponsor. One inbox, and a real person comes back to you.</p>
          <p><strong>And a promise: MPower doesn't sell sponsorships, run ads, or carry affiliate deals inside the communities.</strong> Partnerships are about contribution and reach, never selling to the room.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="mailto:askme@mpowerhq.nz">askme@mpowerhq.nz <span class="arr">→</span></a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <hr class="rule" />
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="mono accent">§ 02 · The founder</span>
          <h2 class="heading contact-col-title">Want to find out more about our founder?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="prose">
          <p>MPower is built by <strong>Lisa Shaw</strong> - a recovering accountant who has run businesses, made payroll with no cash in the bank, sat on boards, and sat at kitchen tables with farming families. The whole reason MPower exists is the question she keeps asking: how do we equip people so they're genuinely empowered, then get out of the way?</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://nz.linkedin.com/in/lisajshaw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find Lisa on LinkedIn <span class="arr">→</span></a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <GreenBlock kicker="§ The promise">
    <h2>Nobody is ever <em>selling you anything</em> in here.</h2>
  </GreenBlock>

</Base>

<style>
  .kicker { color: var(--c-spring); margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .contact-h1 { font-size: var(--t-h1); max-width: 14ch; }
  .contact-lede { margin-top: 32px; max-width: 56ch; opacity: .9; }
  .contact-ctas { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 64px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .contact-col-title { font-size: var(--t-h4); margin-top: 14px; max-width: 18ch; }

  .prose { max-width: 64ch; }
  .prose p { margin-top: 16px; opacity: .88; line-height: 1.7; }
  .prose p:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose strong { color: var(--c-mist); font-weight: 600; }
  .prose a:not(.btn) { color: var(--c-spring); }
  .prose a:not(.btn):hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .prose .btn { margin-top: 24px; }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  }
</style>
